## External API Keys
# 1inch API key for DEX aggregation (Get from: https://portal.1inch.dev)
ONEINCH_API_KEY=your-1inch-api-key-here

## Private Keys (NEVER commit real keys!)
# For contract deployment only - use a testnet wallet with minimal funds
PRIVATE_KEY=your-private-key-here

## CORS Configuration
# Allowed frontend origins (comma-separated for multiple)
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173,http://localhost:3000

## Rate Limiting
# Requests per minute per IP
RATE_LIMIT_PER_MINUTE=100

## Logging
# Log level: debug, info, warn, error
LOG_LEVEL=info
